Megatron walks towards the control room, and hears Astroblast. "Good, stay
there, and be ready". He then shouts through his comm-link, "Motormaster,
Scourge, Cyclonus and Switchblade, meet me in the control room. Astroblast.
If Autofire returns, tell him to meet me here too".
